<p begin="00:01:14.490" end="00:01:18.350" style="s2"><span style="s4">ausbildungs</span> curriculum der</p>
<p begin="00:01:16.049" end="00:01:21.259" style="s2">bundesärztekammer<span style="s3"> die</span> notwendige</p>
